125
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,733
Mei Jiejie is in the Emperor's favor right now

126
00:06:24,733 --> 00:06:28,333
Palace of Shattered Jade is cold and remote. It's not suitable for a patient to live here.

127
00:06:28,333 --> 00:06:31,967
I brought you some silver charcoal. Just use them for the moment.

128
00:06:31,967 --> 00:06:35,100
