131
00:06:41,033 --> 00:06:44,567
I've been sick for a long time 
It's no wonder that they don't treat me as well

132
00:06:44,567 --> 00:06:46,000
It's better to have one less problem than one more

133
00:06:47,233 --> 00:06:48,567
Not to mention since you're in favor right now

134
00:06:48,567 --> 00:06:50,267
