136
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:57,133
Bring me something when I need it desperately. Nothing can compare to this favor.

137
00:06:57,933 --> 00:06:59,600
It's all because you have a good personality

138
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:03,633
You can even tolerate Kang Fuhai's leave. He is such an ungrateful thing

139
00:07:03,633 --> 00:07:05,600
Since he is ungrateful,

140
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,100
