167
00:08:25,057 --> 00:08:26,450
As long as you like it

168
00:08:26,450 --> 00:08:28,742
I like it

169
00:08:28,742 --> 00:08:30,149
It's almost the end of the year

170
00:08:30,149 --> 00:08:31,535
