189
00:09:32,733 --> 00:09:34,917
Because we are like sisters,

190
00:09:34,917 --> 00:09:36,610
I can't tell them

191
00:09:36,610 --> 00:09:38,337
There's always a possibility

192
00:09:38,337 --> 00:09:40,048
